Dialogue: 99,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna hide and seek,\Ngather around me and speak!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:03.94,0:00:06.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I do! I wanna!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:04.74,0:00:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Do I deserve to join them?"
Dialogue: 99,0:00:06.45,0:00:08.86,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let me in!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lost in that thought,
Dialogue: 99,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.37,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's the matter, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the girl was left alone,\Nhaving botched her chance to participate.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:17.79,0:00:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the school picnic,
Dialogue: 99,0:00:19.08,0:00:19.96,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here you go!
Dialogue: 99,0:00:19.63,0:00:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the lonely girl traded parts \Nof her lunch with her teacher.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With no club activity to keep her busy,\Nshe comes straight home.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.85,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And here, we'll stir-fry it a bit.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:35.35,0:00:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only messages she receives\Nare from either her parents or advertisers.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's a lot of vegetables,
Dialogue: 99,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.73,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}so you can probably make it quickly \Nif you cut them in advance.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:41.73,0:00:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That girl is me, Hitori Gotoh,\Nin my first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:42.73,0:00:44.36,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can probably do that \Nin the morning, yeah.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.99,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lately I've gotten good at making \Nso many dishes so quickly
Dialogue: 99,0:00:46.99,0:00:49.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought I didn't need to know any more,
Dialogue: 99,0:00:47.53,0:00:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes I wonder if this is really the life I want to lead.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:49.49,0:00:52.37,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but lately I'm learning once again \Nhow interesting cooking can be.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:52.74,0:00:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But like, I freeze at\Nthe first syllable when I speak,
Dialogue: 99,0:00:56.83,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I can't look people in the eye.
Dialogue: 99,0:00:59.04,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this introverted life suits me just fine.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.25,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Personally I like a lot of options with rice.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:02.25,0:01:05.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, of course. But you—
Dialogue: 99,0:01:02.79,0:01:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You watching this?
Dialogue: 99,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:06.88,0:01:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the kind of kid who pretended \Nto read at the back of the classroom.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:11.72,0:01:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no friends.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:13.55,0:01:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And look at you now! \NYou're part of one of the hippest bands out there.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even introverts have\Na chance to shine in a band.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 99,0:01:24.31,0:01:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please give a warm welcome to\NIn Storms performing Trigger.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:35.16,0:01:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's up?
Dialogue: 99,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad, lend me your guitar!
Dialogue: 99,0:01:38.45,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 99,0:01:43.04,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, Hitori's getting into guitar too!
Dialogue: 99,0:01:49.46,0:01:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could someone like me\Nshine like them if I started a band?
Dialogue: 99,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 99,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do it! I'm going to master the guitar!
Dialogue: 99,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll form a school band and...
Dialogue: 99,0:02:14.78,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,E, A, G? Why is it teaching me the alphabet?
Dialogue: 99,0:02:23.71,0:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll perform at the school festival,
Dialogue: 99,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and everyone will go crazy for me!
Dialogue: 99,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy... for me?
Dialogue: 99,0:04:29.04,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I put in six hours of practice a day\Nso I could play before a crowd. I never quit.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:35.13,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet middle school was over before I knew it.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't perform.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.89,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the school festival!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recruited zero people.
Dialogue: 99,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.64,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As band members!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Didn't even make any friends to begin with!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.52,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For three whole years!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time, for sure...
Dialogue: 99,0:04:50.85,0:04:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}High school is where\NI'll form my freakin' band!
Dialogue: 99,0:04:56.32,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fast forward a month after that declaration.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:00.11,0:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm this close to becoming a hermit,\Nthe guitar my only salvation.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:08.83,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lyrics and composition: me.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From my closet with love.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:14.04,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But before the neighbours report\Nmy shitty song as late night noise pollution,
Dialogue: 99,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should upload my latest \Ncover from that hit band.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been some time since\NI took my dad's suggestion
Dialogue: 99,0:05:25.89,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and uploaded my guitar videos\Nunder the handle {\i0}guitarhero{\i1}.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My previous video has been getting comments.
Dialogue: 99,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been racking up the views lately, too,
Dialogue: 99,0:05:38.32,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and people are telling me I'm good...
Dialogue: 99,0:05:40.11,0:05:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe it's okay if I can't handle real life!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tons of people cheering for me online!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The internet is filled with socially \Nanxious introverts just like me!
Dialogue: 99,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I formed a band and played this at our school fe—
Dialogue: 99,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I put the effort in, okay?
Dialogue: 99,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought CDs to school \Nand set them on my desk.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk to me!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I flaunted my band merch.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk to me!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I put in a song request at lunch...
Dialogue: 99,0:06:09.35,0:06:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This next song was requested by\NClass 2-A's Gotoh-san.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...for the death metal song I was into at the time.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 99,0:06:16.27,0:06:19.99,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna gonna gonna\Npulverise your skuuuuull!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:21.99,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The flashbacks won't stop!\NGet out! Out of my head!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Performing must be so nice.
Dialogue: 99,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 99,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That could work!
Dialogue: 99,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I look... super cool!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:02.61,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm already a total rocker chick!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I look like a real {\i0}somebody{\i1}!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The people can't look away!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:09.95,0:07:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone's just gotta talk to me now!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:14.58,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna be all over \Nthis year's culture festival!
Dialogue: 99,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So, about that corgi's butt.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where are we next?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Science room B.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, wanna karaoke after this?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:39.56,0:07:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah, I'm down.
Dialogue: 99,0:07:40.65,0:07:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You sure?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wonder what I should sing...
Dialogue: 99,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did my midnight high make me overdo it?
Dialogue: 99,0:07:54.33,0:07:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm putting out such \Npowerful rocker chick vibes...
Dialogue: 99,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe they just didn't want to approach me?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:00.84,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no, no!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm having a mental breakdown!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at that!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If they're laughing at me, \Nit won't just be a mental breakdown,
Dialogue: 99,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be mental annihilation!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, it's so cute, I've gotta laugh!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A guitar?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My day's immediately better!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kita-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kita-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. What's up?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, I know.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:27.07,0:08:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't expect to put the onus solely on \Nother people and get the results I want.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:33.24,0:08:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyone here must be wallowing\Nin their solitude like me.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet that guy's separated from—
Dialogue: 99,0:08:39.04,0:08:40.08,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Papa!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.71,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sorry to keep you waiting, dear.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.88,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, no problem.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:44.88,0:08:45.84,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, let's grab dinner!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:45.38,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're the perfect freakin' family!
Dialogue: 99,0:08:45.84,0:08:48.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What would you like?
Dialogue: 99,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry for assuming\Nyou were miserable like me.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:53.43,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I passed 30,000 subs.
Dialogue: 99,0:08:57.35,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, online is where I truly belong.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:02.69,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorta makes me not wanna go back to school...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I spy a guitar!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:12.24,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a guitar, right?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:13.70,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you play?!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I haven't talked to anyone\Nin so long, my voice is—
Dialogue: 99,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sorry to ambush you.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nijika Ijichi, a second year\Nat Shimo-Kitazawa High.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitori Gotoh. Shuka High. First-year.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, Hitori-chan...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right to first names, are we?!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How well can you play?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty decent, I guess...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:38.60,0:09:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So like, I'm in a bit of a pinch here.
Dialogue: 99,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do it, that's okay, but...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Like really, it'd be fine, I'm just kinda stuck...
Dialogue: 99,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing okay about her!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:48.33,0:09:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut right to the chase!
Dialogue: 99,0:09:50.27,0:09:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, won't you help\Nmy band out just for today?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Band?
Dialogue: 99,0:09:57.37,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a gig later today, \Nbut our guitarist just ditched us!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The song's not too hard! \NYou'll pick it up right away!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}A gig? Later today?!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please say yes!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:06.13,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uhh...
Dialogue: 99,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whaaaaaaaaaat!?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:10.51,0:10:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Let's head to the club!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't even said anything yet!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got dragged along.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:19.85,0:10:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You come to Shimo-Kitazawa often?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, no.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:23.77,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right, like I've got the guts to visit \Nthe cool people fashion district...
Dialogue: 99,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost to the club.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, Nijika-chan's pretty fashionable herself.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's got the {\i0}real{\i1} rocker-chick vibe.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, I'm in a drab tracksuit,
Dialogue: 99,0:10:38.91,0:10:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a real bear of a set of bags under my \Neyes, and a back as arched as a cat...
Dialogue: 99,0:10:41.58,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bet I smell like moldy closet too,\Ngiven how I'm always in mine.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I smell like mothballs.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Nijika-chan here? She smells amazing.
Dialogue: 99,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She smells just the way \Na high school girl should!
Dialogue: 99,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, am I walking too fast?
Dialogue: 99,0:10:56.97,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 99,0:10:58.18,0:11:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The club we're playing at \Ntoday is called Starry.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.69,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Playing at a club...
Dialogue: 99,0:11:02.10,0:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My big sister's the manager there.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:05.02,0:11:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That sounds weirdly legit.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, what's my heart doing?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I work part-time there.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Hitori-chan, are you the athletic type?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:19.12,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not really, though I'm somehow\Nalways the last one standing in dodgeball.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm about to perform at a club.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh god, my feet are going cold.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:32.09,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think of the festival\Nperformance you've been dreaming of!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:36.22,0:11:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that comes my solo tour!\NAt a ZEPP! Or the Super Arena!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitori! Hitori! Hitori!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the girl who sold out the Budokan...
Dialogue: 99,0:11:46.77,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 99,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:50.19,0:11:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please don't regret asking me!
Dialogue: 99,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might regret having asked her.
Dialogue: 99,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are! This is the place.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:00.53,0:12:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I descending into hell?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My first club...
Dialogue: 99,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so dark... So stuffy...
Dialogue: 99,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-It's so relaxing.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:16.01,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:19.01,0:12:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No you're not!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could we ask the PA to record again?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:21.18,0:12:23.51,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's the band that's playing today.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought bands would be intimidating,
Dialogue: 99,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.31,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They might be a little older than us?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:25.31,0:12:27.89,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}After they're done, we'll rehearse too.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:25.31,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but they're all indoorsy, shy introverts!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like me.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:30.19,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's the PA-san.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my arrogance!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:39.74,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryo!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:41.45,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hitori Gotoh-chan, a guitarist\NI miraculously met at the park!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eeep, is she staring me down?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet our bassist, Ryo Yamada.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hitori Gotoh!\NI'm terribly sorry for offending you!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:54.88,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 99,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're okay!
Dialogue: 99,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo's just not the expressive type.
Dialogue: 99,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to call her weird! She likes it!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She totally does.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, about the manager...
Dialogue: 99,0:13:06.72,0:13:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She told us to practice until we're up.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:09.02,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, she stormed out in a rage\Nto buy things after you snuck off.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head to the studio before she comes back!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reality's a scary beast.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:24.66,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I feel like there's \Nsomething exciting just up ahead!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's today's setlist and sheet music.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:33.46,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where are the other members?
Dialogue: 99,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everyone!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be playing instrumentals for this gig.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:40.59,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I can handle this song.
Dialogue: 99,0:13:43.72,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll need to make up for\Nthe lack of vocals with our skill,
Dialogue: 99,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but all those people said I'm \Ngood at guitar, so I can pull it off!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I can!
Dialogue: 99,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she King Kong?
Dialogue: 99,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe they'll be blown away by my playing!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:00.57,0:14:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, I've gotten pretty great... \Nerr, pretty decent reception online.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.86,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's take it right from the top.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:02.86,0:14:06.62,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's your first time, \Nso we'll run through slow,
Dialogue: 99,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I even have 30,000 subscribers!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:06.62,0:14:09.04,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}then we can speed it up \Nas you get used to it.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do this!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:26.64,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She sucks!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-How can I suck?
Dialogue: 99,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm {\i1}guitarhero{\i0}!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got 30,000 subscribers!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to explain!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:36.94,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Timing yourself to others \Nis of vital importance in a band!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hitori has social anxiety \Nand can't make eye contact,
Dialogue: 99,0:14:43.99,0:14:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so she'll be inclined to \Nrush ahead of the others!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be an awesome solo player,
Dialogue: 99,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a band she's rock bottom,\Nbelow even water fleas!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:52.04,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there, this is Plankton Gotoh.
Dialogue: 99,0:14:54.29,0:14:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's acting like a washed up comedian!
Dialogue: 99,0:14:57.38,0:15:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, Hitori Gotoh turned to dust,\Nnever to hold a guitar again.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, please!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The show's about to start!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I-I-I can't do this!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault! \NWe just got together today!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm very good either.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}very{\i0} good.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:24.28,0:15:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at me, please?\NCome back down to Earth!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm completely incapable of emceeing, too.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:32.66,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know, I can offer up my life\Nand put on a harakiri show!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-They'll at least remember\Nthe name of the band then, right?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for sucking!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:40.92,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not rock, that's metal!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:43.46,0:15:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bonk anyone who\Nheckles you with my bass.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Does bonking someone with a bass \Nmake that kind of sound?
Dialogue: 99,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, bloodshed is pretty rockin'.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Super rockin'.
Dialogue: 99,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much rocking going on!
Dialogue: 99,0:15:55.77,0:16:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the only people coming to\Nwatch us are probably my friends.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:00.19,0:16:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Nijika's my only friend, so...
Dialogue: 99,0:16:03.61,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No normal high school girl \Ncould tell if we were trash!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'd so get ratioed if she said that online.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? So just chill!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:13.16,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done...
Dialogue: 99,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd certainly know if we sucked or not.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah but you're not normal, Ryo.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that wasn't a compliment.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 99,0:16:23.63,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't force her.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for pushing you into this.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I, no, that isn't it!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:32.97,0:16:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was really happy that you approached me.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:37.73,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to start a band,\Nbut couldn't ever get anyone to join.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just upload covers \Nto the internet instead.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you normally play?
Dialogue: 99,0:16:48.24,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned pretty much every \Nhit from the last few years,
Dialogue: 99,0:16:51.24,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could play them right away \Nonce the band got together...
Dialogue: 99,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 99,0:16:55.33,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I mean, look at how I am now.
Dialogue: 99,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this band stuff was just a pipe dream after all...
Dialogue: 99,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You only cover the hits, huh...
Dialogue: 99,0:17:05.38,0:17:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like {\i1}guitarhero{\i0}! Ever heard of her?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.68,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's probably about our age, I think...
Dialogue: 99,0:17:09.26,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}guitarhero...
Dialogue: 99,0:17:11.68,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you a link if you haven't!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She's crazy good! You should hear her!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crazy... good?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She comes up in my recommendations \Na lot, so I've seen her too.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got chops.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:25.15,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!? That name's kinda cringe though.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it?
Dialogue: 99,0:17:29.95,0:17:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I subscribed and even turned on\Nnotifications for her channel!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to play with her someday!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, you just did.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:38.12,0:17:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what I'm trying to say is,
Dialogue: 99,0:17:41.29,0:17:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,every big guitarist was practicing \Ntheir butt off behind the scenes,
Dialogue: 99,0:17:44.75,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,even when there wasn't \Nan audience in sight for them.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out {\i1}guitarhero{\i0}'s stuff later!
Dialogue: 99,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll get what I mean after that.
Dialogue: 99,0:17:54.68,0:18:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't think anyone\Nin the real world cared about me.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:02.48,0:18:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up on this band thing \Njust because today didn't go well!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that we're just kind of, you know.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:08.32,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of what?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:11.07,0:18:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet here's someone who's cared about me,\N watched over me, and reached out to {\i0}me{\i1}.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She got up.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:18.79,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This miracle may never repeat itself.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let it go to waste!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I, umm.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you change your mind?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:34.43,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I have to do this,\Nbut I'm still scared stiff!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:37.85,0:18:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The audience's stares will smite me where I stand!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're so afraid,\Nhow about playing with this?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is just like my own setup at home!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of place do you live in?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:51.61,0:18:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How you feelin' tonight, Shimo-Kita!
Dialogue: 99,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's perked up a little.
Dialogue: 99,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what should we call you on stage?
Dialogue: 99,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is plain old Hitori-chan alright with you?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No thanks...
Dialogue: 99,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Any nicknames, then?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:05.75,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me "hey you" and \N"you there" a lot in middle school...
Dialogue: 99,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think those are nicknames!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:10.88,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew anyone well enough \Nto get nicknames from them!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no friends... Hitori botched it.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling her a loner is even worse!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bocchi the loner here!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:23.31,0:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She likes it.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had a nickname before.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're turning into a sob story...
Dialogue: 99,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You never told me your band's name, by the way.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:30.90,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ack!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Kessoku Band.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kessoku Band... as in a cable tie?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:41.74,0:19:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impec-{\i1}cable{\i}.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}intolerable{\i0}! We are so changing it!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? Doesn't it sound cute?
Dialogue: 99,0:19:46.58,0:19:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 99,0:19:48.92,0:19:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll discuss the name later!\NIt's time to get on stage!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:54.84,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is to have fun, even if you suck!
Dialogue: 99,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause your feelings \Ncome through in your playing, see?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We can focus on the technical stuff next time!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:07.02,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:09.52,0:20:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:10.77,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 99,0:20:12.65,0:20:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a next time for me!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do? We're Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:22.24,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be playing a few tunes\Nyou probably know today!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the box?
Dialogue: 99,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I kinda hate that I'm not at my best right now,
Dialogue: 99,0:20:41.55,0:20:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but playing together \Nin a band is really fun!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never felt like a star until today...
Dialogue: 99,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I still don't!
Dialogue: 99,0:20:53.73,0:20:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact I may have even reached a new low!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, did I screw up a lot!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:02.95,0:21:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You bungled an introduction, too.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you're freaking me out!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:12.25,0:21:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll strive to be able to greet\Nmy classmates by our next gig!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda declaration is that?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's come so far.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:22.43,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's kick off the Bocchi-chan welcome party\Nplus performance review!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:27.10,0:21:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough socializing \Nfor today, so I'll be heading home.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:30.27,0:21:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 99,0:21:31.85,0:21:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 99,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pardon me!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:34.15,0:21:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This cable tie's not holding\Nanything together!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get over my social anxiety
Dialogue: 99,0:21:51.29,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring out my full {\i1}guitarhero{\i0} powers!
Dialogue: 99,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For Nijika-chan,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:58.05,0:21:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for Ryo-san,
Dialogue: 99,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and for Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 99,0:22:02.84,0:22:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 99,0:23:38.48,0:23:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tune in next week!
